%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Left%20For%20Classes%2C%20Never%20Returned'%3A%2030%20Go%20Missing%20In%203%20Months%20In%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKavita%2C%20the%20wife%20of%2047-year-old%20Atom%20Samarendra%20Singh%2C%20is%20fearing%20the%20worst.%20On%20May%206%2C%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20massive%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20researcher%20and%20social%20worker%2C%20went%20missing.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20news%20of%20him%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20who%20was%20with%20him%20--%2048-year-old%20Yumkhaibam%20Kirankumar%20Singh%20--%20has%20not%20returned%20either.%20The%20two%20had%20driven%20to%20the%20Saheibung%20area%2C%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Manipur%20Olympic%20Park%2C%20bordering%20the%20foothills%20of%20Kangpokpi%20district.%20Their%20cellphones%20are%20switched%20off.%20They%20are%20untraceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2030%20people%20have%20gone%20missing%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May.%20Given%20the%20number%20of%20missing%20complaints%20and%20the%20un-numbered%20First%20Information%20Reports%20filed%2C%20the%20number%20can%20grow%20by%20leaps%20and%20bounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20searches%20are%20conducted%20after%20a%20missing%20complaint%20is%20filed%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20success%20yet.%20Sources%20said%20there%20are%20over%206%2C000%20Zero%20FIRs%2C%20so%20the%20number%20of%20people%20missing%20can%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20wanted%20his%20son%20becomes%20a%20scientist.%20The%20family%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20to%20Shillong%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20worked%20very%20hard%20and%20wanted%20me%20to%20join%20the%20ISRO's%20young%20scientist%20programme%20held%20in%20Shillong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh's%20son%20Atom%20Thoihenba%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20our%20son%20to%20study%20in%20Delhi.%20How%20will%20I%20manage%20that%20now%20because%20he%20was%20the%20only%20earning%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20families%20should%20at%20least%20be%20given%20samples%20for%20DNA%20test%20so%20we%20can%20perform%20the%20last%20rites.%20But%20the%20Manipur%20government%20cannot%20do%20that%20and%20cannot%20find%20the%20missing%20persons%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh's%20uncle%20Atom%20Meghajit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExactly%20two%20months%20after%20the%20journalist%20and%20his%20friend%20went%20missing%2C%20another%20tragedy%20unfolded%20in%20Imphal%20on%20July%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHijam%20Luwangbi%20Linthoingambi%2C%2017%2C%20had%20left%20her%20home%20for%20her%20NEET%20coaching%20classes%20when%20the%20curfew%20was%20relaxed%20in%20the%20morning.%20She%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20her%20boyfriend%20%E2%80%93%2017-year-old%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20two%20went%20for%20a%20long%20ride%20on%20his%20bike%2C%20thinking%20the%20situation%20was%20improving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20missing%20since.%20Their%20parents%20have%20filed%20complaints%20at%20two%20separate%20police%20stations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20police%20say%20there%20is%20CCTV%20footage%20confirming%20they%20were%20spotted%20going%20towards%20Nambol%20area%20in%20Imphal%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCybercrime%20police%20reports%20that%20her%20phone%20was%20last%20switched%20off%20at%20Kwakta%20and%20the%20boy's%20phone%20got%20switched%20off%20at%20Lamdan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hijam%20Kullajit%2C%20father%20of%20the%20girl.%20The%20two%20places%20are%20located%20in%20two%20different%20districts%20--%20Kwakta%20in%20Bishnpur%20district%2C%20Lamdan%20in%20Churachandpur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%2018%20km%20away%20from%20each%20other.%20The%20areas%20at%20the%20border%20of%20the%20valley%20and%20hills%20have%20seen%20major%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20she%20didn't%20return%2C%20I%20called%20her%20and%20she%20picked%20up.%20She%20seemed%20frightened%20and%20said%20she%20was%20in%20Nambol.%20I%20asked%20why%20she%20was%20a%20Nambol%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20reveal%20her%20location%2C%20so%20her%20father%20can%20come%20and%20pick%20her%20up.%20She%20murmured%20Khoupum%20(20%20km%20from%20Nambol)%20and%20her%20phone%20got%20switched%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20girl's%20mother%20Jayashree%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20are%20fearing%20that%20their%20loved%20ones%20are%20being%20tortured.%20Hemanjit's%20cellphone%20is%20now%20being%20used%20with%20a%20new%20number%2C%20the%20police%20have%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20area%20is%20just%2010%20km%20inside%20from%20the%20main%20road...%20the%20Tiddim%20road%2C%20but%20the%20police%20does%20not%20dare%20to%20go%20there%20to%20search%2C%26quot%3B%20Phijam%20Ibungobi%2C%20Hemanjit's%20father%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hills%2C%20the%20civil%20society%20has%20documented%20missing%20cases%20and%20also%20cases%20where%20the%20bodies%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20sent%20back.%20A%20mass%20burial%20has%20been%20planned%20on%20August%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20reports%20of%2044%20dead%20bodies%20of%20our%20people%20who%20went%20missing%20and%20are%20now%20in%20the%20morgues%20of%20Imphal%20hospitals.%20We%20have%20requested%20the%20authorities%20to%20send%20those%20bodies%20for%20burial%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20spokesperson%2C%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690915020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ft3e9h6no_moreh-violence-manipur-240-_625x300_26_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-30-people-missing-in-manipur-in-3-months-families-shattered-4260696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kavita%2C%20the%20wife%20of%2047-year-old%20Atom%20Samarendra%20Singh%2C%20is%20fearing%20the%20worst.%20On%20May%206%2C%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20massive%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20a%20journalist%2C%20researcher%20and%20social%20worker%2C%20went%20missing.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20news%20of%20him%20since.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-30-people-missing-in-manipur-in-3-months-families-shattered-4260696%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-30-people-missing-in-manipur-in-3-months-families-shattered-4260696%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-30-people-missing-in-manipur-in-3-months-families-shattered-4260696%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Civic%20Body%20Employees%20Got%20Salaries%20On%201st%20Day%20Of%20Month%3A%20AAP's%20Dig%20At%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20all%20MCD%20employees%20received%20their%20salaries%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20month%20as%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20honest%20government%20in%20the%20municipal%20corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20in%20Hindi%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20do%20in%2013%20years%2C%20we%20did%20it%20in%20just%20five%20months.%26quot%3B%20The%20AAP%20ended%20the%20BJP's%2015-year%20tenure%20in%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20after%20its%20victory%20in%20the%20civic%20polls%20held%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%202010%2C%20today%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20municipal%20corporation%2C%20from%20the%20commissioner%20to%20a%20peon%2C%20from%20a%20sweeper%20to%20a%20teacher%2C%20from%20a%20gardener%20to%20a%20DBC%20(domestic%20breeding%20checkers)%20worker%2C%20everyone%20is%20getting%20salary%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20s