re%20was%20no%20official%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20clamp%20Article%20355%20on%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20said%20he%20received%20the%20reply%20via%20email%20on%20August%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20before%20filing%20the%20RTI%20application%2C%20Ajay%20Kumar%20had%20also%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%20petitioning%20her%20to%20intervene%20in%20controlling%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CManipur%20may%20be%20a%20small%20state%2C%20but%20it%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20our%20Union.%20However%2C%20recent%20events%20makes%20it%20appear%20that%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%20of%20which%20you%20are%20the%20Supreme%20Head%2C%20does%20not%20consider%20Manipur%20to%20be%20worthy%20of%20attention%E2%80%A6.sending%20the%20central%20forces%20without%20giving%20them%20the%20operational%20independence%20to%20tackle%20the%20emergency%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20like%20asking%20a%20child%20to%20draw%20with%20just%20paper%20and%20no%20crayons%E2%80%A6am%20writing%20to%20you%20as%20a%20citizen%20and%20a%20patriot%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20underlined%20by%20Kumar%2C%20the%20categorical%20reply%20of%20the%20MHA%20is%20in%20contradiction%20to%20widespread%20reporting%20in%20the%20media%20two%20days%20after%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20invoked%20Article%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Article%20355%2C%20the%20MHA%2C%20as%20per%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-govt-leaves-out-lok-sabha-question-on-article-355-in-manipur-report%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoting%20%E2%80%98sources%E2%80%99%20then%2C%20had%20made%20two%20crucial%20appointments%20to%20take%20control%20of%20the%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%20While%20Ashutosh%20Sinha%2C%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(Intelligence)%2C%20had%20been%20appointed%20by%20MHA%20on%20May%205%20night%20as%20the%20overall%20operational%20commander%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20Kuldip%20Singh%2C%20former%20DGP%20(CRPF)%2C%20had%20been%20named%20as%20security%20adviser%20to%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20who%20is%20also%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20move%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20from%20controlling%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20acting%20partisan%20and%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20community%2C%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20head%20of%20state%20police%2C%20at%20a%20press%20meet%20in%20Imphal%20then%2C%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20imposed%20Article%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20based%20on%20which%20Singh%20had%20been%20appointed%20the%20security%20adviser%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20that%20official%20statement%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-mysterious-case-of-the-imposition-of-article-355-in-manipur%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%2C%20had%20underlined%20the%20mysterious%20case%20of%20clamping%20the%20Article%20without%20clamping%20Article%20356%20on%20Manipur.%20Never%20in%20Indian%20political%20history%20has%20Article%20355%20been%20imposed%20on%20a%20state%20without%20Article%20356%20which%20brings%20a%20state%20formally%20under%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20August%201%2C%20too%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Athouba%20Khuraliam%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20powerful%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisation%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Unity%20(COCOMI)%20which%20is%20seen%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.youtube.com%252Fplaylist%253Flist%253DPLzia1qLN9v2Abtxt-_mFc9_38ia0mdkfM%26psig%3DAOvVaw1uvk8m8QvXjud1W1AoHGhm%26ust%3D1690985782219000%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3Dvfe%26opi%3D89978449%26ved%3D0CBIQjRxqFwoTCIjp2pfTu4ADFQAAAAAdAAAAABAE%5C%22%3Estated%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kuldip%20Singh%20had%20been%20controlling%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state%20since%20after%20%E2%80%9CCentre%20had%20taken%20control%20of%20it%E2%80%9D%20and%20therefore%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20handling%20other%20divisions%20of%20state%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20latest%20RTI%20reply%20of%20the%20MHA%20stating%20that%20it%20has%20no%20information%20about%20issuing%20any%20notification%20on%20using%20Article%20355%20in%20any%20state%20till%20June%2013%2C%202023%2C%20strongly%20indicates%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20law%20and%20order%20is%20still%20technically%20under%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%2C%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20355%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuty%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20protect%20States%20against%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%E2%80%9D.%20It%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shall%20be%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20protect%20every%20State%20against%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20of%20every%20State%20is%20carried%20on%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20claims%20of%20%E2%80%98double-engine%E2%80%99%20government%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20despite%20so%20many%20reports%20of%20mayhem%20and%20violence%2C%20this%20indicates%20that%20the%20state%20is%20fully%20under%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%3C%