20benefits%20of%20biodiversity%20commerce%20with%20locals%20and%20also%20decriminalises%20biodiversity%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20amends%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20Act%2C%202002%2C%20was%20passed%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20with%20a%20voice%20vote.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20cleared%20the%20legislation%20on%20July%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20for%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20said%20the%20bill%20is%20aimed%20at%20providing%20benefits%20to%20tribal%20and%20local%20communities%20by%20simplifying%20processes.%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20want%20to%20promote%20Ayush%20and%20Ayurved%20and%20for%20that%20purpose%20we%20brought%20this%20amendment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20legislation%20the%20government%20is%20simplifying%20the%20compliance%20burden%20while%20encouraging%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20research%20and%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20would%20also%20help%20in%20simplifying%20the%20patent%20application%20process%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20objective%20is%20to%20widen%20the%20scope%20of%20access%20benefit%20sharing%20with%20local%20communities%2C%20which%20is%20the%20main%20thing%20and%20the%20conservation%20of%20the%20biological%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20aims%20at%20encouraging%20cultivation%20of%20medicinal%20plants%20and%20removing%20compliance%20burden%20on%20Indian%20companies%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20objective%20is%20also%20to%20decriminalise%20the%20offences...%20to%20reduce%20the%20fear%20among%20the%20stakeholders%20for%20effective%20compliance%2C%26quot%3B%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20on%20December%2016%2C%202021.%20It%20was%20later%20moved%20to%20a%20joint%20committee%20on%20December%2020%2C%202021%2C%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20the%20amendments%20favoured%20industry%20and%20contradicted%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Convention%20on%20Biological%20Diversity%20(CBD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20submitted%20its%20report%20in%20Parliament%20on%20August%202%20last%20year%20with%20the%20recommendation%20that%20the%20bill%20may%20be%20passed%20after%20the%20inclusion%20of%20their%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESulata%20Deo%20(BJD)%2C%20Bhubaneswar%20Kalita%20(BJP)%2C%20Ayodhya%20Rami%20Reddy%20Alla%20(YSRCP)%2C%20GK%20Vasan%20TMC%20(M)%2C%20Ramji%20(BSP)%2C%20Brijlal%20(BJP)%20and%20V%20Vijaysai%20Reddy%20(YSRCP)%20participated%20in%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690910160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Frtvrrj68_parliament-generic-pti_625x300_23_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-4260487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parliament%20on%20Tuesday%20passed%20the%20Biological%20Diversity%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20entails%20provisions%20for%20sharing%20benefits%20of%20biodiversity%20commerce%20with%20locals%20and%20also%20decriminalises%20biodiversity%20offences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-4260487%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-4260487%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-passes-biological-diversity-amendment-bill-4260487%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22No%20Communal%20Ang