arly-4000000-19227200%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20seismologist%20revealed%20that%20Taylor%20Swift%20fans%20in%20Seattle%2C%20Washington%2C%20triggered%20activity%20that%20was%20on%20par%20with%20a%20small%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeismologist%20Jackie%20Caplan-Auerbach%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F07%2F27%2Fentertainment%2Ftaylor-swift-seismic-activity%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20%E2%80%98Swift%20Quakes'%20took%20place%20on%20July%2022%20and%2023%20and%20that%20the%20dancing%20at%20the%20shows%20caused%20seismic%20activity%20%E2%80%98equivalent%20of%20a%202.3%20magnitude%20earthquake.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20activity%20beats%20the%20previous%20record%20in%20Seattle%2C%20which%20was%20generated%20by%20Seattle%20Seahawks'%20fans%20during%20a%20game%20against%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Saints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20shaking%20was%20twice%20as%20strong%20and%20absolutely%20doubled%20it.%20I%20grabbed%20the%20data%20from%20both%20nights%20of%20the%20concert%20and%20quickly%20noticed%20they%20were%20clearly%20the%20same%20pattern%20of%20signals.%20If%20I%20overlay%20them%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other%2C%20they're%20nearly%20identical%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Swift%20also%20become%20the%20first%20living%20artist%20in%20nearly%2060%20years%20to%20have%20four%20albums%20in%20the%20top%2010%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20organization%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690909200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fq6kbbh7o_taylor-swift-concert_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftaylor-swift-gifts-rs-82-lakh-to-each-tour-truck-driver-who-carried-her-equipment-4260385%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20also%20gifted%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20generous%20amou