20is%20seeking%20to%20expand%20beyond%20the%20company's%20biggest%20foreign%20base%20of%20China%20where%20regulatory%20approvals%20for%20expansion%20are%20slow%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chinese%20suppliers%20could%20be%20critical%20if%20Tesla%20were%20to%20establish%20a%20plant%20in%20India%20and%20keep%20costs%20in%20check%20for%20a%20cheap%20EV.%20India%20does%20not%20have%20local%20suppliers%20for%20components%20such%20as%20battery%20cells%2C%20with%20even%20India's%20largest%20EV%20maker%2C%20Tata%20Motors%2C%20importing%20them%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20meetings%20with%20officials%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Tesla%20executives%20informed%20the%20Indian%20government%20that%20it%20would%20like%20to%20have%20some%20of%20its%20vendors%20from%20China%20set%20up%20base%20locally%20to%20boost%20its%20supply%20chain%2C%20three%20Indian%20officials%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20talks%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20officials%20told%20Tesla%20that%20granting%20approvals%20for%20wholly-owned%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20India%20could%20be%20difficult%20due%20to%20intense%20scrutiny%20of%20Chinese%20firms%20since%20a%202020%20border%20clash%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20Indian%20officials%20said%20they%20had%20suggested%20a%20workaround%20in%20which%20Tesla%20would%20emulate%20the%20approach%20of%20Apple.%20The%20U.S.%20smartphone%20giant%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20obtained%20approvals%20to%20bring%20Chinese%20suppliers%20to%20India%20after%20they%20found%20local%20joint-venture%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20the%20trade%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20a%20fast-growing%20supply%20chain%20in%20India%20which%20includes%20Taiwan's%20Foxconn%20assembling%20its%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20been%20approving%20some%20Chinese%20suppliers'%20JV%20partnerships%20with%20Indian%20companies%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis%2C%20one%20of%20the%20government%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20remains%20hesitant%20about%20allowing%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20especially%20automakers%2C%20to%20expand%20in%20the%20country%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20China's%20BYD%20told%20its%20Indian%20partner%20it%20would%20shelve%20a%20new%20%241%20billion%20investment%20plan%20to%20build%20EVs%20there%20after%20its%20investment%20proposal%20faced%20scrutiny%20from%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20specifying%20Chinese%20vendors%2C%20a%20fourth%20source%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20Tesla's%20discussions%20in%20India%20said%20the%20U.S.%20company%20is%20looking%20at%20supply%20chain%20partners%20for%20its%20India%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20Indian%20officials%20said%20pairing%20local%20and%20Chinese%20players%20could%20work%20for%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20ecosystem%20for%20their%20(Chinese)%20vendor%20base%20...%20those%20approvals%20can%20be%20granted%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis%20if%20there%20an%20Indian%20joint%20venture%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690902240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fqseui84_tesla-generic-reuters_625x300_16_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-asks-tesla-to-copy-apple-in-pairing-chinese-indian-suppliers-report-4259492%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Tesla%20examines%20building%20a%20plant%20in%20India%2C%20officials%20have%20asked%20the%20company%20to%20emulate%20Apple%20in%20finding%20local%20firms%20to%20partner%20with%20any%20C