20measure%20of%20labor%20demand%2C%20dropped%2034%2C000%20to%209.582%20million%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20June%2C%20the%20lowest%20level%20since%20April%202021%2C%20the%20Labor%20Department%20said%20in%20its%20monthly%20Job%20Openings%20and%20Labor%20Turnover%20Survey%2C%20or%20JOLTS%20report%2C%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-job-openings-fall-to-more-than-two-year-low-in-june%2Farticleshow%2F102320511.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-job-openings-fall-to-more-than-two-year-low-in-june%2Famp_articleshow%2F102320511.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-job-openings-fall-to-more-than-two-year-low-in-june%2Famp_articleshow%2F102320511.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20NCB%20Busts%20%5C%22Biggest%5C%22%20Darknet%20Drug%20Cartel%20Operating%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20today%20claimed%20to%20have%20busted%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%26quot%3B%20darknet-based%20LSD%20cartel%20operating%20in%20India%20with%20the%20seizure%20of%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20blots%20and%20Rs%2026%20lakh%20in%20cash%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20three%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cartel%20named%20'Zambada'%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20volume%20of%20business%20and%20supply%20chain%26quot%3B%20of%20this%20hallucinogenic%20category%20of%20drug%20and%20is%20also%20operating%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20US%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Canada%2C%20Russia%2C%20Spain%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Greece%20and%20Turkiye%2C%20NCB%20Deputy%20Director%20General%20(operations%20and%20enforcement)%20Gyaneshwar%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cartel%20was%20being%20operated%20by%20young%20educated%20men%20in%20the%20age%20bracket%20of%2021-25%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20second%20LSD%20trafficking%20cartel%20busted%20by%20the%20agency%20in%20the%20last%20about%20three%20months%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20anti-narcotics%20agency%20had%20seized%20a%20cache%20of%2015%2C000%20LSD%20blots%2C%20the%20highest-ever%20catch%20in%20one%20operation%2C%20and%20arrested%20half-a-dozen%20people%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELSD%20or%20lysergic%20acid%20diethylamide%20is%20a%20synthetic%20chemical%20based-drug%20and%20is%20categorised%20as%20a%20hallucinogen.%20It%20is%20abused%20largely%20by%20youngsters%20and%20its%20consumption%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20issues.%20It%20is%20odourless%2C%20colourless%20and%20tasteless%20and%20it%20is%20painted%20on%20small%20squares%20of%20paper%20(blots)%20that%20can%20be%20licked%20or%20swallowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20continued%20operations%2C%20it%20was%20learnt%20that%20the%20largest%20cartel%20operating%20in%20LSD%20on%20the%20darknet%20-%20Zambada-%20operates%20from%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20ground%20operators%20of%20this%20cartel%20were%20identified%20through%20technical%20and%20human%20surveillance%20and%20this%20led%20to%20the%20location%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B%20of%20this%20cartel%20who%20was%20operating%20from%20Ballabgarh%20(Faridabad)%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20Delhi%20zonal%20office%20conducted%20multiple%20raids%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20these%20three%20persons%20leading%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%2013%2C863%20LSD%20blots%2C%20428%20grams%20MDMA%20(ecstasy)%2C%20and%20the%20freezing%20of%C2%A0%20Rs%2026.73%20lakh%20%26quot%3Bdrug%20money%26quot%3B%2C%20agency%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Zambada'%20cartel%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%26quot%3B%20cartel%20in%20the%20country%20with%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3B5-star%20rating%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20NCB%20said%20the%20drug%20cartels%20on%20the%20darknet%20are%20rated%20on%20a%20scale%20of%201-5%20stars%20based%20on%20the%20potency%20of%20the%20drug%20sold%20through%20their%20platform%20and%20their%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20service%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarknet%20refers%20to%20the%20deep%20hidden%20internet%20platform%20that%20is%20used%20for%20narcotics%20sale%2C%20exchange%20of%20pornographic%20content%20and%20other%20illegal%20activities%20by%20using%20the%20secret%20alleys%20of%20the%20onion%20router%20(ToR)%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20surveillance%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20said%20the%20cartel's%20name%20is%20derived%20from%20%26quot%3BIsmael-Marlo%20Zambada%20Garcia%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20Mexican%20drug%20lord%2C%20and%20he%20was%20the%20last%20remaining%20fugitive%20on%20the%20list%20of%20Mexico's%2037%20most%20wanted%20drug%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20carries%20a%20reward%20of%20up%20to%20USD%2015%2C000%2C000%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%20The%20first%20time%20the%20name%20of%20this%20cartel%20was%20reported%20in%20the%20country%20was%20in%20September%202022%20when%20the%20Hyderabad%20Police%20arrested%20eight%20people%20for%20drug%20trafficking%20using%20the%20darknet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NCB%2C%20declared%20on%20the%20darknet%20after%20this%20interdiction%20in%20India%20that%20he%20was%20safe%20and%20will%20never%20be%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarcia%20is%20stated%20to%20be%20in%20%26quot%3Bclose%20contact%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20darknet%20operator%20called-%20Dr%20Seuss%20alias%20DS%20and%20TS%20(Tribe%20Seuss)%20or%20Gamma%20Goblin-%20who%20is%20the%20largest%20source%20of%20LSD%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Zambada'%20intended%20to%20open%20an%20Indian%20%26quot%3Boutlet%26quot%3B%20of%20Dr%20Seuss%20with%20a%20minimum%20stock%20of%20one%20lakh%20LSD%20blots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20%26quot%3Boutlets%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20USA%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Canada%2C%20Russia%2C%20Spain%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Greece%20and%20Turkiye%2C%20according%20to%20DDG%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Dr%20Seuss)%20had%20already%20started%20recruiting%20people%20for%20this%20purpose%20and%20had%20put%20in%20place%20the%20logistics%20and%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCB%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCB%20said%20it%20is%20working%20to%20unearth%20the%20third%20such%20known%20LSD%20cartel%20operating%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20two%20earlier%20busts%2C%20it%20has%20registered%20a%20total%20of%20six%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%20(NDPS)%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%2022%20Indians%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20operations%20led%20to%20a%20total%20seizure%20of%2029%2C013%20LSD%20blots%20and%20472%20grams%20of%20MDMA%20powder%20and%20the%20freezing%20of%20Rs.51.38%20lakh%20cash%20or%20%26quot%3Bdrug%20money%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cartels%20collect%20money%20in%20various%20crypto%20wallets%20and%20then%20transfer%20it%20across%20through%20various%20layers%20of%20virtual%20currencies%20and%20finally%20receive%20the%20money%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20an%20NCB%20officer%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690899660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fcyber-crime-generic-istock_650x400_81504427706.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-ncb-busts-biggest-darknet-drug-cartel-operating-in-india-4258980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20today%20claimed%20to%20have%20busted%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%26quot%3B%20darknet-based%20LSD%20cartel%20