icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsituation-tense-in-nuh-parts-of-gurugram-after-communal-clashes-haryana-cm-suspects-bigger-conspiracy-top-developments%2Farticleshow%2F102319619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20At%2011%2C500%20Feet%2C%20Air%20Force%20Chopper's%20Daring%20Op%20Near%20Amarnath%20Shrine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complex%20underslung%20operation%20at%2011%2C500%20feet%2C%20a%20Mi-17%20V5%20helicopter%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20successfully%20airlifted%20a%20stranded%20civilian%20helicopter%20from%20the%20Panchtarni%20helipad%20near%20the%20Amarnath%20shrine%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20visual%20of%20the%20helicopter%20airlifting%20a%20helicopter%20shared%20by%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20shows%20the%20Mi-17%20transport%20helicopter%20lifting%20the%20underslung%20damaged%20chopper%20from%20the%20helipad%20and%20manoeuvered%20through%20the%20valley%20that%20lies%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20holy%20Amarnath%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20could%20allow%20a%20very%20little%20margin%20of%20error%20since%20a%20heavy%20load%2C%20the%20As-350%20helicopter%2C%20was%20attached%20to%20the%20air%20force%20chopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mi-17%20navigated%20through%20steep%20mountains%20on%20either%20side%20and%20successfully%20carried%20out%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20displayed%20immaculate%20planning%2C%20systematic%20preparation%20and%20exceptional%20flying%20skills%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Panchtarni%20helipad%20is%20now%20open%20to%20ferry%20pilgrims%20after%20being%20blocked%20because%20of%20the%20damaged%20chopper.%20It%20was%20airlifted%20to%20the%20Neelgrar%20helipad%20by%20the%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20began%20on%20July%201.%20The%2062-day%20pilgrimage%20will%20culminate%20on%20August%2031.%20The%20pilgrims%20travel%20through%20two%20traditional%20routes%20--%20Baltal%20and%20Pahalgam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20air%20force%20carried%20out%20a%20similar%20operation%20in%20Kedarnath%2C%20where%20two%20Mi-17%20V5s%20airlifted%20a%20crashed%20private%20chopper%20from%20the%20Kedarnath%20helipad%2C%20located%20at%2011%2C500%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20troops%20have%20to%20be%20airlifted%20to%20a%20battlefield%20or%20stranded%20civilians%20have%20to%20be%20evacuated%2C%20the%20Mi-17%20V5%20forms%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20air%20force's%20major%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690897560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F8ch881i8_mi17-airlift-650_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-air-force-chopper-airlifts-helicopter-near-amarnath-shrine-4259665%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20complex%20underslung%20operation%20at%2011%2C500%20feet%2C%20a%20Mi-17%20V5%20helicopter%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20successfully%20airlifted%20a%20stranded%20civilian%20helicopter%20from%20the%20Panchtarni%20helipad%20near%20the%20Amarnath%20shrine%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-air-force-chopper-airlifts-helicopter-near-amarnath-shrine-4259665%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-air-force-chopper-airlifts-helicopter-near-amarnath-shrine-4259665%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-air-force-chopper-airlifts-helicopter-near-amarnath-shrine-4259665%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Arjun%20Tendulkar%20Shines%20In%20Deodhar%20Trophy%2C%20Outsmarts%20Batter%20Cleverly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Arjun%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F