5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%2C%20which%20made%20it%20apparent%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20not%20in%20the%20XI.%20When%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20whether%20Kohli%20was%20playing%20or%20not%2C%20Pandya%20gave%20this%20answer%3A%20%26quot%3BTwo%20changes%20for%20us.%20Ruturaj%20comes%20in%20place%20of%20Umran%20and%20Unadkat%20comes%20in%20place%20of%20Axar.%20Going%20to%20the%20decider%20the%20boys%20are%20pumped%20up%20and%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20game.%20Looks%20good%20(the%20surface)%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20much%20will%20change%2C%20batting%20first%20gives%20a%20good%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20set%20a%20good%20total.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20management's%20decision%20to%20rest%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20in%20the%20second%20ODI%2C%20that%20India%20lost%2C%20did%20not%20go%20down%20well%20with%20several%20experts.%20Speaking%20on%20Jio%20Cinema%2C%20former%20India%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aakash%20Chopra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F597-aakash-chopra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAakash%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20pleased%20with%20the%20experimentation%20and%20felt%20the%20senior%20duo%20did%20not%20require%20rest%20for%20this%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20why%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20were%20rested%3B%20they%20haven't%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20because%20if%20you%20see%2C%20after%20WTC%20final%20there%20was%20a%20break%20of%20three%20weeks%20and%20there%20was%20only%20seven%20days%20of%20play%20in%20the%20India-WI%20tests.%20After%20that%20you%20play%20one%20ODI%20and%20leave%20the%20next.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20T20s%20aside%2C%20leave%20it.%20I%20mean%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20play%20T20s%20this%20year%2C%20how%20is%20it%20going%20to%20affect%20anyone%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20T20%20WC%20this%20year.%20Rohit%20and%20Kohli%20anyway%2C%20do%20not%20feature%20in%20T20Is.%20So%2C%20you%20are%20relaxing%20just%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20relaxing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20batter%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Nayar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F974-abhishek-nayar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Nayar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20believes%20that%20the%20strongest%20team%20should%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20since%20the%20time%20you%20are%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20away%20from%20a%20big%20tournament%2C%20you%20should%20play%20with%20your%20strongest%20eleven%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20an%20injury.%20Play%20with%20them%20only%20because%20once%20you%20do%20that%2C%20everyone%20gets%20to%20know%20each%20other's%20strengths%20and%20it%20will%20help%20you%20to%20experience%20playing%20together%20in%20different%20situations%20and%20learn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20(Playing%20XI)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E(w)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108591-ruturaj-gaikwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanju%20Samson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1701-sanju-samson-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanju%20Samson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C