n%3ERai%20also%20spoke%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20committee%20named%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%20One%20Police%20Uniform.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20six%20MPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rai%20said%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Chintan%20Shivir%20of%20Home%20Ministers%20of%20States%20organised%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20on%2027-28th%20October%202022%2C%20it%20was%20suggested%20to%20the%20States%20to%20consider%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Police%20Uniform%20to%20create%20a%20distinct%20identity%20of%20police%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20citizens%20easily%20recognize%20police%20personnel%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20six%20MPs%20who%20asked%20the%20question%20are%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20breakaway%20faction%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20said%20that%2024%20states%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20government%20on%20this%20and%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20in%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Police%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Development.%20This%20committee%20has%20some%20members%20of%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%2C%20representatives%20of%20Textile%20Research%20Associations%2C%20the%20Troop%20Comforts%20Limited%20and%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standard%20(BIS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20and%20law%20and%20order%20is%20a%20state%20subject%20in%20the%20state%20list%20of%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20clarity%20yet%20on%20what%20the%2024%20states%20have%20said%20in%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolice%20reform%20has%20been%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20well%20as%20activists.%20Conditions%20in%20custody%2C%20methods%20of%20investigation%2C%20treatment%20of%20witnesses%20and%20also%20prevention%20of%20custodial%20deaths%2C%20ensuring%20better%20and%20fair%20treatment%20of%20all%20citizens%20has%20been%20widely%20discussed.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20passed%20a%20judgement%20on%20September%2022%2C%202006%20in%20Writ%20Petition%20(Civil)%20No.310%20of%201996%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EPrakash%20Singh%20and%20others%20vs%20UOI%20and%20others%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20on%20several%20issues%20concerning%20police%20reforms%20and%20issued%20seven%20specific%20directives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20said%2C%20police%20uniform%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffive-simple-yet-powerful-reforms-to-make-indian-police-force-effective%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20seldom%20been%20the%20focus%20of%20police%20reform%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUniforms%20in%20each%20state%20are%20distinct%20and%20a%20often%20bear%20a%20historical%20imprint%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20evolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690887670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F03115116%2Fdownload-16.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-police-uniform-committee-constituted-home-ministry-in-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Police'%20is%20on%20the%20state%20List%20and%20a%20state%20subject%20but%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20last%20year%2C%20at%20a%20%E2%80%98Chintan%20Shivir%E2%80%99%20it%20has%20proposed%20a%20single%20uniform%20for%20all%20states.%20Responses%20from%2024%20states%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20made%20public.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-police-uniform-committee-constituted-home-ministry-in-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Is%20Stuck%20and%20India%20Is%20Stuck%20Next%20to%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160903%2Fusama-tayyab-ivNmrA2Vg8g-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20coalition%20has%20announced%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1765127%5C%22%3Eintent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20complete%20its%20tenure%20in%20August%2C%20triggering%20national%20elections.%20Intra-coalitional%20bargaining%20continues%20over%20the%20wisdom%20of%20dissolving%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20officially%20ends%20at%20midnight%20on%20August%2012.%20If%20the%20government%20dissolves%20before%20that%20date%2C%20a%20caretaker%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pakistani.org%2Fpakistan%2Fconstitution%2Fpart8.ch2.html%5C%22%3E90%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20oversee%20a%20national%20election.%20If%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20waits%20until%20its%20constitutional%20term%20is%20complete%2C%20then%20the%20caretaker%20government%20has%20just%2060%20days%20for%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty%20days%20makes%20little%20difference%2C%20but%20the%20PML-N%20leadership%20appears%20to%20believe%20some%20added%20time%20will%20buy%20space%20for%20the%20economy%20to%20improve%20and%20perhaps%20for%20more%20wind%20to%20blow%20against%20the%20PTI%20loyalists%20left%20standing%20with%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan.%20Others%20in%20the%20coalition%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1764997%2Fpolitical-parleys-on-the-menu-as-pm-meets-allies%5C%22%3Efear%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20time%20might%20encourage%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20indulge%20in%20a%20constitutional%20pause%20on%20elections%20so%20it%20can%20caretake%20for%20longer%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20much%20longer.%20Bangladesh%E2%80%99s%20experience%20with%20a%20caretaker%20government%20in%202006%2C%20which%20ultimately%20opted%20(with%20military%20backing)%20to%20govern%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20instead%20of%20its%20allotted%2090%20days%2C%20may%20be%20on%20such%20skeptics%E2%80%99%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20old%20PTI%20has%20splintered%20under%20the%20duress%20it%20has%20faced%20since%20the%20May%209%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20where%20PTI%20protests%20nationwide%20devolved%20into%20property%20destruction%20including%20on%20military%20installations.%20Politicians%20from%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20provincial%20base%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20where%20the%20PTI%20has%20governed%20either%20solely%20or%20in%20coalition%20since%202013%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1765262%5C%22%3Edefected%3C%2Fa%3E%20en%20masse%20from%20their%20former%20captain.%20These%20are%20not%20mere%20back%20benchers%20but%20include%20two%20former%20PTI%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20province%20and%20at%20least%20one%20former%20provincial%20cabinet%20minister.%20This%20most%20recent%20news%20merely%20adds%20to%20the%20number%20of%20PTI%20leaders%20who%20have%20opted%20to%20retire%2C%20leave%20politics%2C%20or%20switch%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20with%20others%20still%20in%20detention%20for%20their%20alleged%20roles%20in%20the%20May%209%20incident%20or%20other%20purported%20wrongdoings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20charisma%2C%20the%20PTI%20could%20have%20been%20organised%20around%20party%20workers%20and%20loyalists.%20But%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2Fj.ctv10crdkk.9%5C%22%3Eopted%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20to%20rely%20on%20electable%20politicians%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20whom%20had%20switched%20parties%20repeatedly%20in%20their%20careers%20%E2%80%93%20to%20vault%20more%20quickly%20to%20national%20power%20with%20military%20support%20in%202018.%20This%20decision%20has%20been%20the%20original%20sin%20that%20has%20facilitated%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20vulnerability%20now%20that%20it%20faces%20military%20ire.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20Khan%20retains%20his%20enormous%20loyalty%20with%20the%20public%20is%20unclear.%20Yet%20whether%20Khan%20voters%20will%20have%20enough%20plausible%20candidates%20to%20vote%20for%20at%20the%20polls%20seems%20even%20further%20in%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%202018%20PTI%20coalition%20was%20more%20fragile%20than%20it%20sometimes%20appeared%20to%20outside%20observers%20and%20PTI%20diehards.%20Winning%20less%20than%20a%20third%C2%A0of%20the%20national%20vote%20and%20with%20PTI%20requiring%20partners%20to%20secure%20a%20national%20assembly%20majority%2C%20small%20headwinds%20against%20the%20party%20always%20threatened%20it%20in%20a%20re-election.%20It%20now%20faces%20a%20gale%20from%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20predicament%20is%20considerable.%20Its%20sickly%20economy%20has%20been%20rehabilitated%20by%20currency%20infusions%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20and%20rich%20Gulf%20countries%20but%20absent%20any%20meaningful%20macro-%20or%20microeconomic%20changes%20that%20will%20alter%20its%20poor%20underlying%20economic%20health.%20It%20continues%20to%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20climate-induced%20disasters.%20The%20US%20withdrawal%20from%20Afghanistan%20has%20not%20improved%20its%20security%20predicament%20as%20some%20anti-American%20Pakistani%20skeptics%20had%20suggested.%20Instead%2C%20Pakistan%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1765402%5C%22%3Estruggles%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20growing%20Afghan%20safe%20haven.%20While%20few%20expect%20the%20security%20situation%20to%20return%20to%20the%20dire%20days%20of%20the%20late%202000s%20or%20early%202010s%2C%20the%20number%20of%20attacks%20on%20the%20periphery%20has%20notably%20increased%20and%20it%20is%20a%20reasonable%20fear%20that%20core%20cities%20may%20not%20be%20far%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20economy%20has%20flourished%20in%20the%20past%20only%20with%20international%20patronage%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20prospect%20for%20that%20seems%20distant%2C%20too.%20While%20international%20donors%20have%20indicated%20through%20their%20recent%20behaviour%20that%20they%20will%20not%20permit%20a%20Pakistani%20economic%20collapse%2C%20there%20is%20no%20apparent%20interest%20in%20returning%20to%20prior%20peaks%20of%20funding.%20The%20US%20is%20profoundly%20dissatisfied%20with%20its%20erstwhile%20ally.%20China%E2%80%99s%20own%20sluggish%20economy%20along%20with%20the%20poor%20performance%20of%20many%20Chinese%20projects%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20likely%20to%20slow%20substantially%20the%20macroeconomic%20impacts%20of%20Chinese%20investments%20in%20its%20all-weather%20friend.%20Many%20of%20the%20most%20capable%20Pakistanis%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2390704%2Fcountrys-brain-drain-situation-accelerated-in-2022%5C%22%3Eleaving%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20with%20emigration%20tripling%20in%202022%20compared%20to%20(pandemic-reduced)%202020%20and%202021%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20first%20visited%20South%20Asia%20in%202002.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FNY.GDP.PCAP.KD%3Fend%3D2022%26locations%3DPK-BD-IN%26start%3D2005%5C%22%3EWorld%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Pakistanis%20earned%20more%20on%20average%20than%20their%20Indian%20and%20Bangladeshi%20peers.%20Since%20that%20time%2C%20the%20income%20of%20the%20average%20Pakistani%20has%20increased%20perhaps%2060%25%20in%20real%20terms.%20Yet%20in%20that%20same%20period%20the%20income%20of%20an%20average%20Indian%20has%20increased%20by%20150%25%20and%20that%20of%20the%20average%20Bangladeshi%20has%20shot%20up%20by%20more%20than%20160%25.%20The%20average%20Pakistani%20now%20makes%20the%20least%20of%20the%20big%20three%20subcontinental%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20such%20economic%20and%20political%20troubles%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20focused%20inward%20for%20the%20last%20several%20years.%20It%20pursued%20quiet%20talks%20with%20India%20that%20produced%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20February%202021%20%E2%80%93%20no%20doubt%20facilitated%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20desire%20to%20manage%20a%20growing%20China%20threat%20by%20tamping%20down%20violence%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20frontier.%20Yet%20while%20Pakistanis%20expected%20the%20ceasefire%20to%20be%20a%20prelude%20to%20bilateral%20political%20engagement%2C%20those%20subsequent%20steps%20never%20took%20place.%20The%20extent%20to%20which%20this%20was%20because%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20hesitations%20or%20internal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-india-modi-visit-general-bajwa-hamid-mir-journalist%5C%22%3Ecivil-military%20clashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20Pakistan%20is%20not%20fully%20known.%20What%20does%20seem%20apparent%20is%20none%20of%20the%20major%20political%20or%20military%20actors%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20invested%20in%20rapprochement%20with%20India%20or%20vice%20versa.%20There%20are%20signs%20the%202021%20ceasefire%20is%20fraying%20%E2%80%93%20with%20complaints%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fradio.gov.pk%2F25-04-2023%2Farmed-forces-fully-prepared-for-befitting-response-of-any-indian-aggression-ispr%5C%22%3Eboth%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Floc-infiltration-attempts-on-the-rise-army-foils-multiple-bids-seeks-to-prevent-militancy-revival-in-kashmir-101687891202355.html%5C%22%3Esides%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20adherence%20to%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20agreement%20may%20be%20less%20than%20complete.%20With%20few%20other%20avenues%20to%20signal%20displeasure%2C%20the%20ceasefire%20could%20collapse%20with%20just%20one%20large%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20continues%20to%20exhibit%20what%20sociologist%20Laurent%20Gayer%20has%20referred%20to%20in%20other%20contexts%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FKarachi%2FBklRBAAAQBAJ%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%3Eordered%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Despite%20nearly%20continuous%2C%20high-stakes%20political%20contestation%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20players%20and%20the%20terrains%20of%20their%20confrontation%20have%20shown%20a%20significant%20level%20of%20continuity%E2%80%9D%20for%20decades.%20The%20same%20players%20play%20the%20same%20game%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%2C%20all%20while%20the%20country%20fails%20to%20advance%20much%20even%20while%20it%20avoids%20collapse.%20None%20expect%20that%20elections%2C%20if%20they%20take%20place%20in%202023%2C%20will%20produce%20any%20meaningful%20deviation%20from%20the%20political%20status%20quo.%20Whether%20the%20PPP%20or%20PML-N%20or%20PTI%20defectors%20secure%20sufficient%20votes%20to%20head%20the%20coalition%2C%20the%20same%20personalities%20will%20play%20the%20same%20game%20of%20musical%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20stuck%2C%20and%20India%20is%20stuck%20next%20to%20Pakistan.%20It%20would%20be%20easy%20for%20observers%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20conclude%20that%20this%20repetitious%20mess%20should%20be%20ignored.%20Analyst%20Happymon%20Jacob%20recently%20stressed%20that%20observers%20must%20know%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20no%20longer%20locked%20into%20a%20strategic%20competition%20with%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%20India%E2%80%99s%20new%20agenda%20is%20about%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20not%20Pakistan.%20This%20is%20no%20doubt%20true%20at%20some%20level%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20so%20easy%20to%20escape%20neighbors.%20If%20Islamabad%20and%20Rawalpindi%20conclude%20they%20have%20gained%20little%20from%20the%20ceasefire%20and%20opt%20to%20divert%20some%20of%20the%20ire%20of%20angry%20young%20Islamists%20toward%20India%2C%20Kashmir%20could%20again%20heat%20up.%20Can%20the%20Indian%20counterinsurgency%20grid%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20quash%20such%20problems%3F%20Perhaps%2C%20but%20with%20an%20active%20China%20frontier%20and%20Manipur%20aflame%2C%20it%20is%20hardly%20a%20proposition%20that%20anyone%20should%20be%20eager%20to%20test.%20India%E2%80%99s%20capabilities%20are%20growing%20but%20they%20are%20not%20so%20great%20that%20it%20can%20easily%20manage%20trouble%20in%20the%20west%20and%20the%20east%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20That%20will%20require%20careful%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChristopher%20Clary%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20University%20at%20Albany%2C%20State%20University%20of%20New%20York%2C%20and%20a%20nonresident%20fellow%20of%20the%20Stimson%20Center%E2%80%99s%20South%20Asia%20program%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20His%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Difficult%20Politics%20of%20Peace%3A%20Rivalry%20in%20Modern%20South%20Asia%3Cem%3E%2C%20was%20published%20by%20Oxford%20University%20Press%20in%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690887648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160903%2Fusama-tayyab-ivNmrA2Vg8g-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-is-stuck-and-india-is-stuck-next-to-it%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20capabilities%20are%20growing%20but%20they%20are%20not%20so%20great%20that%20it%20can%20easily%20manage%20trouble%20in%20the%20west%20and%20the%20east%20at%20the%20same%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-is-stuck-and-india-is-stuck-next-to-it%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20New%20Novel%20Considers%20What%20It%20Means%20to%20Be%20a%20Muslim%20in%20Today%E2%80%99s%20India%20And%20Can't%20Come%20Up%20With%20Answers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01155958%2FDAEFC20B-9E9E-4268-B054-A64E9B81.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20decades%20after%20it%20was%20published%2C%20Ahmed%20Ali%20reflected%20on%20the%20genesis%20of%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETwilight%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20novel%20dealing%20with%20the%20capital%E2%80%99s%20social%20climate%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%20%E2%80%9CA%20tide%20of%20revolt%20led%20some%20of%20us%20to%20contemplate%20the%20state%20of%20inanity%20and%20indifference%20into%20which%20the%20social%20order%20had%20sunk%2C%E2%80%9D%20felt%20Ali.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20purpose%20in%20writing%20the%20novel%20was%20to%20depict%20a%20phase%20of%20our%20national%20life%20and%20the%20decay%20of%20a%20whole%20culture%2C%20a%20particular%20mode%20of%20thought%20and%20living%2C%20values%20now%20dead%20and%20gone%20before%20our%20eyes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20359px)%2085vw%2C%20359px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01154620%2F912ybSbumfL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22359%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01154620%2F912ybSbumfL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20656w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01154620%2F912ybSbumfL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-197x300.jpg%20197w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666108%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22547%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98History%E2%80%99s%20Angel%2C%E2%80%99%20Anjum%20Hasan%2C%20Bloomsbury%20India%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnjum%20Hasan%E2%80%99s%20new%20novel%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20seems%20inspired%20by%20a%20similar%20impulse.%20It%20is%20a%20calm%2C%20measured%20portrayal%20of%20a%20character%20whose%20Janus-like%20nature%20is%20to%20look%20backwards%20even%20as%20he%20is%20compelled%20to%20walk%20forwards.%20This%20is%20the%20mild-mannered%20Alif%2C%20a%20history%20schoolteacher%20who%20subjects%20every%20free%20moment%20to%20a%20historical%20test%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20now%20but%20how%20was%20it%20back%20then%3F%20Or%20that%20was%20then%20but%20how%20does%20it%20matter%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20his%20students%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20drive%20home%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20difference%20between%20history%20and%20story%E2%80%9D%20while%20being%20aware%20that%20%E2%80%9Cour%20stories%20are%20still%20swollen%20with%20the%20exaggerations%20that%20make%20some%20men%20impossibly%20broad-chested%20and%20lion-hearted%20and%20the%20rest%20just%20men%E2%80%9D.%20During%20a%20school%20trip%20to%20Humayun%E2%80%99s%20Tomb%2C%20one%20of%20his%20pupils%20addresses%20him%20with%20a%20religious%20slur%20and%2C%20instinctively%20and%20uncharacteristically%2C%20Alif%20responds%20by%20reaching%20out%20and%20twisting%20his%20ear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reverberations%20of%20this%20act%20are%20the%20framework%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20novel.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20not%20simply%20a%20linear%20progression%20of%20events%3A%20it%20is%20an%20informed%20exploration%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20milieu%2C%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20providing%20the%20necessary%20shades%20and%20contrasts%20for%20a%20portrayal%20of%20a%20cross-section%20of%20Muslims%20in%20north%20India%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20on%20this%20spectrum%20of%20faith%20and%20hope%20include%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Tahira%2C%20a%20store%20manager%20at%20a%20Karol%20Bagh%20supermarket%20who%20is%20studying%20for%20an%20MBA%20and%20whose%20weekends%20are%20given%20over%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20which%20makes%20the%20world%20go%20round%2C%20or%20so%20say%20Dale%20Carnegie%20and%20Steven%20Covey%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20teenage%20son%20often%20puzzles%20Alif%20by%20his%20fascination%20with%20technology%20and%20the%20digital%20world%2C%20as%20does%20the%20attitude%20of%20his%20practical%20cousin%2C%20owner%20of%20a%20shoe%20store%2C%20who%20dreams%20of%20moving%20to%20the%20Emirates%20and%20urges%20Alif%20to%20manage%20the%20shop%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%20ripples%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20existence%20arrive%20in%20the%20form%20of%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20tempestuous%20life%20of%20his%20close%20friend%20Ganesh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20bit%20too%20fond%20of%20the%20bottle.%20Ganesh%20nurtures%20feelings%20for%20an%20old%20school%20crush%20and%2C%20to%20his%20surprise%2C%20Alif%20finds%20himself%20feeling%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20ageing%20parents%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20do%20the%20best%20they%20can%20to%20survive%20in%20changing%20circumstances.%20Much%20of%20their%20time%20is%20spent%20in%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20relatives%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20their%20increasingly%20radicalised%20domestic%20help.%20The%20rest%20is%20spent%20in%20watching%20cooking%20shows%20and%20news%20on%20TV%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20inevitably%20posing%20the%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20it%20mean%2C%20sir%2C%20to%20be%20a%20Muslim%20in%20contemporary%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20lives%20are%20suffused%20by%20a%20feeling%20that%20Orhan%20Pamuk%20once%20described%20as%20%3Cem%3Eh%C3%BCz%C3%BCn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20melancholy.%20This%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20softens%20the%20view%20%E2%80%9Clike%20the%20condensation%20on%20a%20window%20when%20a%20teakettle%20has%20been%20spouting%20steam%20on%20a%20winter%E2%80%99s%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20and%20beyond%20these%20characters%20is%20the%20city%20of%20Delhi%20itself%2C%20which%20Hasan%20portrays%20in%20hues%20that%20alternate%20between%20the%20gaudy%2C%20the%20shop-worn%20and%20the%20materialistic.%20Her%20characters%20move%20through%20the%20teeming%20streets%20and%20residences%20of%20the%20old%20city%2C%20survey%20the%20grandeur%20of%20its%20monuments%2C%20and%20test%20themselves%20against%20the%20brashness%20of%20its%20ritzy%20malls%20and%20new%20habitations.%20Delhi%2C%20thinks%20Alif%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20city%20on%20which%20the%20apocalypse%20descends%20every%20day%20and%20the%20city%20where%20the%20apocalypse%20is%20always%20awaited%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c.jpeg%20886w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666112%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20this%20is%20extremely%20well%20done%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20immersing%20the%20reader%20in%20varieties%20of%20minority%20experience.%20In%20particular%2C%20there%20is%20the%20discomfiting%20scene%20of%20Alif%20and%20Tahira%20undergoing%20a%20derogatory%20interrogation%20while%20trying%20to%20rent%20a%20flat.%20At%20another%20time%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20told%20that%20Tahira%20dislikes%20the%20assumption%2C%20especially%20during%20Eid%2C%20that%20because%20she%20is%20Muslim%20and%20a%20woman%20she%20must%20be%20a%20great%20cook.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20all%20we%20are%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks%20Alif.%20%E2%80%9CBawarchis%3F%20Poetry-spouting%20fools%20with%20minced%20mutton%20coming%20out%20of%20our%20ears%2C%20thinking%20only%20of%20Allah%20and%20pining%20only%20for%20bahisht%20between%20mouthfuls%20of%20zafrani%20pulao%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20flip%20side%20of%20this%20is%20that%20there%20are%20stretches%20in%20which%20very%20little%20happens%20from%20a%20novelistic%20point%20of%20view.%20Instead%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20relies%20on%20creating%20empathy%20through%20well-rounded%20characters%20to%20propel%20itself%20forward%20by%20sinuous%20sentences.%20Because%20Alif%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20rather%20read%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Discovery%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20discover%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20complaisant%20nature%20isn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20up%20to%20the%20job%20of%20sustaining%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20one%20stage%2C%20Alif%20politely%20informs%20his%20overly%20patriotic%20school%20principal%20while%20breaking%20into%20a%20sweat%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20Muslim%20history%20of%20India%E2%80%A6try%20separating%20Muslims%20from%20Hindus%20in%20this%20way%20when%20you%20go%20into%20the%20past%20of%20this%20country%20and%20all%20you%20find%20are%20entanglements%E2%80%9D.%20Though%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20national%20destiny%20frightens%20him%2C%20he%20has%20little%20choice%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20moderate%20hopes%20and%20incremental%20changes%20that%20democratic%20statehood%20offers%20till%20they%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20substitute%20for%20it%2C%20which%20no%20one%20has%20so%20far%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20ways%2C%20he%20personifies%20the%20novel%E2%80%99s%20title%2C%20taken%20from%20Walter%20Benjamin%E2%80%99s%20conception%20of%20the%20angel%20of%20history%2C%20whose%20face%20is%20turned%20towards%20the%20past%20with%20the%20wreckage%20of%20catastrophe%20piled%20at%20his%20feet.%20The%20angel%20wants%20to%20restore%20what%20has%20been%20smashed%20but%20cannot%2C%20because%20his%20wings%20are%20entangled%20in%20the%20storm%20of%20progress%20that%20propels%20him%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20careful%20delineation%20of%20such%20a%20predicament%2C%20Anjum%20Hasan%20asks%20us%20to%20consider%20what%20is%20gained%20and%20what%20is%20lost%20in%20the%20face%20of%20this%20nationalistic%20storm.%20The%20novel%20is%2C%20to%20borrow%20from%20Susan%20Sontag%2C%20an%20education%20of%20the%20heart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsanjay-sipahimalani%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Sipahimalani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20Mumbai-based%20writer%20and%20reviewer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690886307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01155958%2FDAEFC20B-9E9E-4268-B054-A64E9B81.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fanjum-hasan-historys-angel-muslim-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anjum%20Hasan%E2%80%99s%20book%20'History%E2%80%99s%20Angel'%20immerses%20the%20reader%20in%20a%20range%20of%20quotidian%20minority%20experiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fanjum-hasan-historys-angel-muslim-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hiccupping%20giant%20panda%20caught%20on%20camera%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690885317000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F966E%2Fproduction%2F_130601583_p0g44686.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-66372950%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Video%20from%20China%E2%80%99s%20Sichuan%20province%20shows%20the%20animal%20looking%20relaxed%2C%20but%20unimpressed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A517%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-china-66372950%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Silence%20Over%20Manipur%20Lays%20Bare%20the%20Crisis%20of%20Indian%20Identity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01150618%2FC48CE12B-72F4-4594-98C6-DDD5E2178AF8_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20took%20a%20chilling%20video%20of%20women%20%E2%80%93%20stripped%20naked%2C%20paraded%2C%20groped%20and%20raped%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20horrifying%20saga%20of%20brutal%20violence%20and%20toxic%20re-territorialisation%20in%20Manipur%20to%20receive%20some%20nation-wide%20attention.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20was%20there%20a%20prolonged%20silence%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20reason%20is%20the%20partisan%20role%20of%20the%20government%20that%20tried%20to%20suppress%20the%20truth%20about%20Manipur%20under%20military%20suppression%20and%20internet%20shutdown.%20Second%20is%20its%20own%20criminal%20silence%20and%20complicity%20in%20stoking%20the%20fires%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fexplainer-manipur-violence-biren-singh-meiteis-kuki-zo-nagas%5C%22%3Epatronising%20of%20violent%20mobs%20of%20one%20ethnicity%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20a%20third%20factor%20is%20equally%20significant.%20States%20and%20regions%20like%20Manipur%20that%20are%20territorially%20peripheral%2C%20have%20a%20different%20and%20contested%20history%20and%20have%20endured%20long%20drawn%20militarised%20conflict%2C%20exist%20as%20peripheries%20in%20the%20imagination%20of%20Indian%20nationhood.%20They%20are%20simply%20seen%20as%20territorial%20spatial%20units%20that%20need%20to%20be%20surveilled%20and%20securitised%20under%20military%20repression%20while%20its%20people%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20disposables%20for%20a%20misplaced%20national%20cause.%20Horrifying%20incidents%20in%20such%20spaces%20are%20thus%20viewed%20as%20normal%2C%20ignored%20or%20even%20legitimised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Manipur%2C%20like%20many%20other%20conflict%20zones%20in%20the%20north-east%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20lie%20on%20the%20extreme%20borders%20of%20the%20physical%20boundaries%20and%20memory%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20dehumanising%20violence%20is%20not%20a%20novelty.%20Their%20landscapes%20are%20littered%20with%20stories%20of%20egregious%20human%20rights%20violations%20including%20sexual%20violence%20perpetrated%20both%20by%20the%20state%20and%20the%20non-state%20actors.%20Nation-wide%20outrage%20is%20selectively%20evoked%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20only%20when%20the%20crimes%20are%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20non-state%20actors.%20Those%20committed%20by%20the%20state%20are%20wished%20away%2C%20defended%20and%20sometimes%20even%20celebrated.%20A%20large%20section%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20media%20has%20allowed%20itself%20to%20be%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20perpetuating%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20nation%20in%20which%20the%20people%20from%20these%20areas%20remain%20invisible%2C%20even%20deemed%20%E2%80%98the%20other%E2%80%99%20because%20they%20do%20not%20share%20the%20same%20sense%20of%20history.%20Attempts%20to%20mainstream%20them%20are%20not%20based%20on%20principles%20of%20diversity%20and%20accommodation%20but%20are%20rather%20treated%20as%20battles%20between%20the%20conquerors%20and%20the%20vanquished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%20995w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM-300x159.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20from%20the%20viral%20video%20which%20shows%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20is%20merely%20a%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg.%20More%20reports%20and%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20killings%2C%20displacements%20and%20the%20shocking%20territorialisation%20of%20Manipur%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20have%20now%20begun%20to%20tumble%20out.%20The%20scale%20of%20it%20would%20be%20much%20more%20horrifying%2C%20far%20more%20than%20what%20we%20have%20witnessed%20in%20Delhi%201984%2C%20Gujarat%202002%20and%20Muzaffarnagar%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20these%20previous%20cases%2C%20the%20rioters%20were%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20for%20a%20few%20days%20till%20the%20government%20began%20to%20act.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20mobs%20had%20a%20free%20for%20all%20situation%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20because%20Manipur%20is%20imagined%20to%20be%20an%20appendage%20and%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20whole.%20The%20Meitei%20majority%20had%20been%20weaponised%20against%20the%20Kuki%20tribals%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98alien%E2%80%99%20even%20within%20this%20restive%20state%20%E2%80%93%20revealing%20that%20there%20exist%20more%20layers%20of%20exclusion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClashes%20have%20now%20abated%20but%20tensions%20persist%20%E2%80%93%20everything%20kept%20well%20under%20the%20garb%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-cant-look-away-from-internet-shutdowns-in-manipur%5C%22%3Eimposed%20internet%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lack%20of%20mobile%20phone%20connectivity%20in%20many%20areas%20and%20a%20disinterested%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attention%20that%20this%20grave%20situation%20has%20received%20so%20far%20is%20too%20little%20and%20too%20disproportionate%20to%20the%20magnitude%20of%20what%20Manipur%20has%20witnessed.%20At%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20outrage%20is%20the%20chilling%20story%20of%20sexual%20assault.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20the%20sexual%20assault%20cases%20merit%20little%20or%20no%20attention%20in%20India%20is%20also%20crucial%20to%20understanding%20the%20deliberate%20silence%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20its%20media.%20It%20took%20digital%20images%20of%20sexually%20assaulted%20tribal%20Kuki%20women%20after%20the%20police%20literally%20fed%20them%20to%20the%20mob%20for%20the%20nation%20to%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20notice.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20even%20after%20the%20horrifying%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20nation%20appears%20to%20be%20divided%20between%20a%20sense%20of%20shame%20and%20whataboutery.%20More%20importantly%2C%20knowledge%20of%20such%20rapes%20and%20sexual%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20were%20not%20unknown%20before%20the%20video%20suddenly%20surfaced.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllegations%20of%20women%20being%20violently%20assaulted%20were%20already%20in%20circulation%20after%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%204.%20Presumably%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20too%20knew%20about%20it%20since%20complaints%20and%20FIRs%20had%20been%20lodged%20in%20the%20police%20stations%20at%20least%20as%20early%20as%20May%2018.%20It%20is%20also%20common%20knowledge%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20are%20used%20as%20weapons%20of%20aggression%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20crisis%20that%20was%20unfolding%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20thus%20calls%20to%20question%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20collective%20conscience%20which%20requires%20disgusting%20images%20for%20incidents%20like%20these%20to%20wake%20us%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-a-complaint-on-the-may-4-assault-was-sent-to-ncw-but-the-complainants-never-got-a-reply%5C%22%3EA%20Complaint%20on%20the%20May%204%20Assault%20in%20Manipur%20Was%20Sent%20to%20NCW%20in%20June.%20But%20It%20Never%20Got%20a%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERapes%20fall%20in%20the%20category%20of%20crimes%20that%20have%20been%20ignored%20and%20swept%20under%20the%20carpet%20through%20deliberate%20intent%20across%20India.%20For%20decades%20after%20independence%20and%20constitutional%20guarantees%20of%20equality%20and%20intolerance%20to%20injustices%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20have%20become%20markers%20of%20male%20machismo%20and%20collective%20triumph%20of%20communities%2C%20often%20with%20the%20tacit%20approval%20and%20encouragement%20by%20women.%20Equally%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20are%20wrongly%20deemed%20as%20repositories%20of%20the%20honour%20of%20the%20family%20or%20the%20community%20they%20belong%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20obsession%20with%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20has%20forbid%20a%20collective%20response%20against%20%E2%80%98defilement%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20bodies%20as%20part%20of%20male%20privilege%20or%20for%20revenge%20and%20humiliating%20the%20other.%20After%20the%20Delhi%20Nirbhaya%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20which%20sparked%20immediate%20nationwide%20outrage%20rape%20finally%20found%20some%20place%20in%20the%20mainstream%20conversations%20and%20national%20discourse.%20However%2C%20the%20empathy%20for%20the%20victim%20and%20outrage%20against%20such%20crimes%20continues%20to%20be%20coloured%20by%20prejudices%20of%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20class.%20It%20is%20rare%20for%20similar%20spontaneity%20and%20outrage%20to%20be%20evoked%20if%20the%20woman%20is%20a%20Dalit%2C%20a%20tribal%20or%20a%20Muslim.%20If%20at%20all%2C%20they%20make%20it%20to%20the%20news%20pages%2C%20it%20is%20left%20to%20the%20few%20feminists%20and%20liberals%20to%20speak%20for%20them.%20Unnao%2C%20Hathras%20and%20Kathua%20rapes%20and%20murders%20are%20cases%20in%20point.%20Sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%20zones%20figures%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20hierarchical%20pyramid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-509290%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMembers%20of%20various%20organisations%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20death%20of%20a%2019-year-old%20Dalit%20woman%20who%20was%20gang-raped%20in%20Hathras%2C%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Friday%2C%20October%202%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESexual%20violence%20and%20conflict%20zones%20with%20disputed%20histories%20thus%20make%20a%20deadly%20combination%20engendering%20in%20the%20national%20conscience%20a%20wilful%20ignorance%20and%20forgetfulness%20of%20the%20troubles%2C%20strife%2C%20traumas%20and%20hopes%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20and%20fragile%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%20Throw%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20led%20government%E2%80%99s%20promotion%20of%20majoritarian%20politics%20of%20exclusion%20across%20the%20country%20and%20you%20have%20a%20virulent%20cocktail%20that%20can%20only%20result%20in%20a%20graver%20disaster.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20push%20and%20his%20partisan%20role%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20has%20brought%20alive%20the%20existing%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20faultlines%20in%20Manipur%20with%20domino%20effect%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20north-east.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manipur%20crisis%20lays%20bare%20a%20national%20crisis%20of%20identity.%20There%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20a%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20ordering%20independent%20probes%20and%20holding%20the%20government%20accountable%20for%20its%20calculated%20indifference%20to%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20blood-soaked%20battleground%2C%20dead%20bodies%2C%20brutalised%20people%2C%20sexually%20assaulted%20women%2C%20burnt%20and%20destroyed%20homes%2C%20displacements%20and%20rigid%20internal%20borders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20for%20redefining%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20and%20re-envisioning%20it%20as%20a%20nation%20where%20the%20conflict%20zones%20that%20lie%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20physical%20boundaries%20do%20not%20simply%20exist%20as%20territories%20to%20be%20controlled%20under%20military%20jackboots.%20An%20inclusive%20India%20cannot%20be%20built%20when%20the%20people%20living%20in%20these%20territories%20continue%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20mere%20expendable%20appendages%20in%20the%20national%20imagination.%20Till%20that%20reimagining%20of%20Indian%20nationhood%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20witness%20many%20Manipur%20like%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20in%20varying%20degrees%20of%20magnitude%20%E2%80%93%20and%20blissfully%20continue%20to%20keep%20them%20under%20the%20wraps%20till%20some%20ugly%20image%20compels%20us%20to%20speak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20Jamwal%20is%20executive%20editor%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20Times%2C%20author%20of%20A%20Dismantled%20State%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story%20of%20Kashmir%20After%20370%20and%20at%20present%2C%20Senior%20JSK%20Journalism%20Fellow%20at%20Stanford%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690883754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01150618%2FC48CE12B-72F4-4594-98C6-DDD5E2178AF8_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-conflict-national-identity-northeast-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Peripheral%20states%20are%20often%20seen%20to%20be%20not%20really%20%E2%80%98Indian%E2%80%99%20and%20to%20be%20held%20by%20militarised%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-conflict-national-identity-northeast-kashmir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%3A%20At%20least%2020%20dead%20and%2027%20missing%20in%20floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690883216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphot