ter%20of%20his%20life%20promises%20to%20be%20as%20fulfilling%20as%20the%20first.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20armed%20forces%20was%20a%20beautiful%20chapter%20in%20itself.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20normal%20tents%20with%20no%20facilities%20or%20attached%20toilets%2C%20etc.%20Today%20I%20have%20realised%20that%20people%20come%20from%20a%20different%20perspective%20where%20they%20want%20luxury%2C%20and%20so%20the%20camps%20have%20now%20changed%20from%20their%20original%20versions%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319285%2Fengineer-turns-land-in-ruins-into-cheese-cottage-homestay-in-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20resorts%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20being%20a%20part%20of%20this%20beautiful%20camping%20experience%20in%20the%20desert%20also%20means%20that%20he%20does%20not%20miss%20his%20Army%20life%20so%20much.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20spend%20some%20of%20my%20time%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20where%20I%20am%20based%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20time%20at%20the%20camps%20in%20Jaisalmer.%20This%20is%20the%20dream.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690811232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdesert-5_11zon-1690808865.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%2024%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20Colonel%20Mahendra%20Mohan%20Prakash%20Singh%20started%20Oasis%20India%20Camp%20to%20help%20tourists%20from%20across%20the%20world%20experience%20the%20magic%20of%20Jaisalmer%E2%80%99s%20desert%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20both%20luxurious%20and%20replete%20with%20adventure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325795%2Fretired-army-officer-colonel-mahendra-mohan-oasis-luxury-camps-in-jaisalmer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Portable%20Innovation%20Saves%20Lives%20by%20Bringing%20Doctors%20to%2030%20Lakh%20Pregnant%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAntenatal%20care%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20pregnancy%20safer%20for%20women%20by%20detecting%20complications%20early%20and%20ensuring%20timely%20treatment.%20At%20least%20four%20antenatal%20care%20visits%20are%20recommended%20to%20monitor%20the%20health%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20and%20her%20fetus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20areas%2C%20about%2054%20percent%20of%20mothers%20attend%20the%20recommended%20visits%2C%20compared%20to%2068.1%20percent%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20implies%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20pregnant%20women%20in%20rural%20regions%20do%20not%20visit%20hospitals%20for%20advised%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20complications%20significantly%20impact%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20In%20India%2C%20there%20were%2097%20maternal%20deaths%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20reported%20between%202018%E2%80%9320.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20such%20deaths%20is%20that%20women%20avoid%20going%20to%20far-off%20healthcare%20centres%20for%20routine%20checkups.%20The%20complications%2C%20if%20any%2C%20remain%20ignored%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Senthil%20Kumar%20Murugesan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh-risk%20mothers%20are%20usually%20identified%20in%20the%20third%20trimester%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20eighth%20month%20of%20pregnancy.%20However%2C%20by%20this%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20late%20to%20effectively%20manage%20complications%20before%20labour.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20fatal%20outcomes.%20Currently%2C%20all%20records%20are%20maintained%20on%20paper%2C%20and%20if%20mortalit