0career%2C%20but%20either%20Whitty%20or%20Marsham%20could%20give%20them.%20He%20is%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20a%20convert%20to%20Muhammadanism%20and%20was%20a%20teacher%20in%20the%20Raj%20School.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20from%20his%20post%20for%20virulent%20attacks%20on%20local%20management%20published%20in%20or%20about%201915%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267482%2Frrr-komaram-bheem-junior-ntr-gond-adivasi-nizam-hyderabad-telugu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20press%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20lives%20in%20Bettiah%20and%20works%20as%20a%20press%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Pratap%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20a%20paper%20which%20distinguished%20itself%20for%20its%20immoderate%20expressions%20on%20Champaran%20Questions%E2%80%A6%20Pir%20Muhammad%20is%20the%20link%20between%20this%20Bettiah%20class%20of%20mostly%20educated%20and%20semi-educated%20men%20and%20the%20next%20class%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Raiyats%E2%80%99%20own%20leaders%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20result%20of%20the%20tyranny%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20never%20forgets%20the%20cries%20of%20the%20just%2C%20and%20the%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%20was%20proof%20of%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mutiny%20ended%20with%20the%20British%20officers%20agreeing%20to%20formulate%20the%20Champaran%20Agrarian%20Act%20of%201918.%20The%20Act%20abolished%20the%20forcible%20cultivation%20of%20indigo%20and%20thus%20relieved%20tremendous%20pressure%20being%20put%20on%20the%20farmers%20here.%20The%20event%20has%20gone%20down%20in%20history%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264216%2Fsaifuddin-kitchlew-freedom-fighter-jallianwala-bagh-hindu-muslim-unity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20major%20revolts%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20forced%20the%20English%20to%20introduce%20a%20Bill%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Tinkathia%20system%20being%20abolished%2C%20the%20farmers%20thought%20the%20worst%20was%20over.%20But%20the%20British%20continued%20to%20oppress%20them%20in%20different%20ways.%20Fuelled%20by%20ending%20this%20once%20and%20for%20all%2C%20Munis%20started%20%3Cem%3ERaiyati%20Sabha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20advocate%20for%20and%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20farming%20community.%20For%20this%2C%20Munis%20faced%20a%20six-month%20jail%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20last%20of%20imprisonment.%20In%201930%20he%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20the%20Patna%20Camp%20jail%20for%20three%20months%20for%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20Salt%20Satyagraha%20of%20the%20Civil%20Disobedience%20Movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20nothing%20could%20deter%20him%20from%20his%20goal%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250530%2Fwoman-freedom-fighter-rani-gaidinliu-northeast-manipur-british-india-independence-inspiring-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotecting%20the%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20countrymen.%20In%201937%2C%20he%20led%20sugarcane%20producers%20who%20were%20protesting%20against%20intermediaries%20who%20were%20pocketing%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20earnings.%20He%20was%20also%20elected%20member%20of%20the%20Champaran%20Zila%20Parishad%20(District%20Board)%20on%20the%20Congress%20ticket%20and%20became%20President%20of%20Bettiah%20Local%20Board%2C%20from%20which%20he%20resigned%20to%20join%20the%20Individual%20Civil%20Disobedience%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20lifetime%2C%20he%20advocated%20for%20rural%20development%2C%20popularisation%20of%20Hindi%20in%20primary%20schools%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20his%20fellow%20Indians.%20Until%20his%20passing%20away%20on%2023%20September%201949%20Munis%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20worth%20looking%20up%20to%20for%20his%20countrymen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELauding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229887%2Fmumbai-rama-khandwala-freedom-fighter-subhas-chandra-bose-national-award-best-tour-guide-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Munis%20on%20his%20passing%20away%2C%20%3Cem%3EPratap%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20Ganesh%20Shankar%20Vidyarthi%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20utmost%20sorrow%20that%20Pir%20Muhammed%20Munis%20of%20Bettiah%2C%20Champaran%20district%20has%20died.%20We%20have%20the%20privilege%20to%20see%20such%20souls%20who%20are%20quietly%20lying%20aside.%20The%20world%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20know%20anything%20about%20their%20issues.%20The%20lesser%20these%20sons%20of%20Mother%20India%20are%20renowned%2C%20the%20more%20profound%20is%20their%20work%2C%20the%20more%20philanthropic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20recited%20the%20dreadful%20story%20of%20Champaran%20to%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20this%20was%20a%20result%20of%20your%20hard-work%20only%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20visited%20Champaran%20which%20made%20this%20land%20a%20pious%20place%20and%20the%20place%20which%20is%20unerasable%20in%20the%20pages%20of%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fon-hindi-diwas-here-s-the-story-of-pir-muhammad-munis-a-hindi-journalist-and-unsung-hero-of-champaran-satyagrah-329625.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20The%20Story%20Of%20Pir%20Muhammad%20Munis%2C%20A%20Hindi%20Journalist%20And%20Unsung%20Hero%20Of%20Champaran%20Satyagraha%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Afroz%20Alam%20Sahil%2C%20Published%20on%2