ble%20to%20train%20them%20properly.%20Women%20are%20not%20encouraged%20to%20look%20at%20driving%20as%20a%20skill%20that%20we%20need%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world.%20That%20is%20the%20socio-cultural%20gap.%20And%20if%20they%20meet%20an%20accident%2C%20women%20go%20into%20panic%20mode%20and%20give%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20I%20know%20how%20to%20drive%2C%20I%20have%20experienced%20confidence%20and%20independence%20while%20I%20am%20on%20the%20road.%20I%20wondered%20why%20not%20offer%20that%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20empowerment%20and%20employment%20to%20women%2C%20instead%20of%20jobs%20that%20restrict%20them%20within%20four%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20transform%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181637%2Fkerala-woman-auto-driver-hero-single-mothers-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emobility%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20started%20MOWO%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteering%20social%20transformation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharathi%20works%20with%20a%20network%20of%20nonprofits%2C%20women%20self-help%20groups%2C%20and%20motor%20vehicle%20manufacturers%2C%20to%20impart%20training%20to%20low-income%20group%20women.%20She%20started%20MOWO%20with%20Rs%205%20lakh%20of%20her%20savings%2C%20and%20has%20been%20pivotal%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20training%20school%20on%20a%201-acre%20land%20in%20the%20city%2C%20established%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Women%20%26amp%3B%20Child%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FMOWO-1-1690463747.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharathi%20has