ckquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20loved%20baking%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20children.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20educator.%20So%2C%20Garhwal%20English%20Medium%20School%20is%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20the%20two%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2065-year-old%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELori%20first%20visited%20India%20in%201998%20for%20a%20school%20field%20trip.%20During%20her%20time%20in%20the%20country%2C%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20children%20living%20on%20the%20streets.%20She%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20So%2C%20a%20year%20later%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20volunteered%20at%20several%20NGOs.%20She%20travelled%20back%20to%20India%20every%20summer%20for%20four%20years%20to%20do%20the%20same%20before%20starting%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20Lori%20returned%20to%20India%20to%20pursue%20PhD%20in%20Landour%20Language%20School.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20my%20thesis%20on%20language%20learning%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20villages%20and%20talk%20to%20people.%20I%20was%20a%20very%20hands-on%20researcher%20and%20wanted%20to%20have%20real%20experiences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20has%20volunteers%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1690289992-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325110%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20125%20students%20studying%20at%20minimal%20fees%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Lori%20Chauhan%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stayed%20in%20Sainji%20during%20the%20research%2C%20where%20she%20met%20her%20husband%20Kunwar%20Chauhan%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20village%20and%20introduced%20himself.%20He%20was%20educated%20in%20Delhi%20but%20chose%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20uplifting%20the%20area.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20in%20common%20besides%20our%20care%20for%20the%20village%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESparks%20flew%20and%20the%20two%20got%20married%20in%202007%2C%20and%20the%20couple%20settled%20in%20Sainji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20a%20year%20into%20our%20marriage%2C%20many%20villagers%20would%20come%20and%20ask%20me%20if%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F264558%2Fengineer-teaches-ipl-cricket-commentary-free-english-language-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20could%20teach%20English%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20children.%20Soon%2C%20they%20started%20requesting%20if%20we%20could%20start%20an%20English%20medium%20school%20for%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20such%20requests%20was%20mostly%20because%20at%20that%20time%20there%20were%20no%20English%20medium%20schools%20nearby%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20in%20Mussoorie%20were%20not%20affordable%20for%20the%20villagers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Garhwal%20English%20Medium%20School%2C%20which%20has%20over%20125%20students%20today%2C%20in%20classes%20starting%20from%20nursery%20to%20Class%208.%20Volunteers%20from%20England%2C%20Canada%20and%20other%20countries%20visit%20the%20school%20often%20as%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEight%20students%2C%20a%20cow%20shed%20and%20teacher%20Aunty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20off%20really%20small%20with%20just%20eight%20students%20in%20a%20makeshift%20classroom%2C%20which%20was%20originally%20a%20cow%20shed.%20But%20this%20arrangement%20did%20not%20last%20long%20as%20we%20started%20to%20get%20more%20and%20more%20students%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20I%20think%20we%20had%20such%20a%20big%20turnout%20was%20because%20the%20people%20here%20want%20to%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%20Their%20children%20who%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98044%2Fproject-kaleidoscope-taranagar-rajasthan-digital-education-piramal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20able%20to%20face%20competition%20from%20children%20from%20private%20schools.%20They%20do%20not%20get%20admission%20to%20good%20colleges%20and%20many%20end%20up%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20villages%20to%20work%20on%20farms.%20The%20parents%20here%20really%20want%20their%20kids%20to%20come%20out%20of%20this%20cycle%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20school%20had%20shifted%20to%20a%20bigger%20building%20with%20more%20teachers%20and%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20runs%20from%20the%20proceeds%20from%20the%20cafe.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-3-1690289913-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325108%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20students%20come%20from%20around%2025%20villages%20in%20the%20Jounpur%20Block%20of%20Tehri%20Garhwal.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Lori%20Chauhan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20hired%20teachers%20from%20nearby%20areas.%20While%20they%20were%20educated%20enough%2C%20their%20method%20of%20teaching%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98jot-this-down-and-memorise-it%E2%80%99%20kind%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20they%20were%20taught%20in%20government%20schools.%20We%20did%20not%20want%20that%20for%20our%20school.%20So%20we%20started%20an%20outreach%20program%20and%20asked%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20come%20and%20share%20their%20methods%20of%20teaching%20with%20our%20teachers%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Lori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20quite%20a%20success%2C%20and%20we%20still%20have%20volunteers%20coming%20in%20from%20different%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20The%20school%20currently%20has%2013%20teachers%2C%20and%20the%20school%20is%20registered%20with%20the%20state%20education%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20important%20aspect%20that%20we%20are%20very%20particular%20about%20is%20that%20all%20the%20learning%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20classrooms%20itself.%20Since%20the%20children%20here%20come%20from%20rural%20backgrounds%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20anyone%20back%20home%20to%20assist%20them.%20So%20we%20ensure%20that%20the%20children%20absorb%20all%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20learnt%20right%20here%20with%20us%20at%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20management%20of%20the%20school%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrior%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20hosted%20travellers%20in%20the%20village%2C%20planned%20activities%20around%20the%20place%2C%20etc%2C%20and%20used%20those%20proceeds%20to%20run%20the%20school.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20we%20could%20not%20proceed%20with%20this%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunwar%2C%20who%20always%20loved%20her%20baking%20skills%2C%20suggested%20they%20open%20a%20bakery%20and%20cafe%20to%20raise%20funds.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20cafe%20came%20into%20existence%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lori.%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20baking%20and%20this%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20idea.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20great%20source%20of%20income%20for%20the%20school%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCj7f9-Us0yV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCj7f9-Us0yV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%