%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnglish%20medium%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Mussoorie%2C%20the%20fee%20is%20enormous%20and%20we%20cannot%20afford%20it.%20The%20school%20and%20Lori%20Aunty%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20blessing%20for%20me%20and%20many%20children%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20education%20here%20is%20as%20good%20as%20any%20private%20school%2C%20and%20we%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20dream%20big%20and%20get%20jobs%20in%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20Lori%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20teacher%20in%20anthropology%20would%20always%20say%20how%20I%20should%20be%20running%20an%20NGO%20instead%20of%20becoming%20a%20professor.%20As%20we%20can%20see%2C%20he%20was%20right.%20The%20path%20my%20life%20took%20is%20so%20much%20more%20fulfilling%20and%20worthwhile%20than%20being%20only%20a%20teacher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESponsorships%2C%20volunteering%2C%20and%20how%20you%20can%20help!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20charge%20a%20very%20minimal%20fee%20of%20Rs%20200%20to%20the%20children%2C%20with%20books%20and%20uniforms%2C%20the%20burden%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20for%20some%20parents.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20run%20a%20sponsorship%20programme%20for%20the%20children%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20program%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20programme%2C%20we%20sponsor%20students%20who%20need%20the%20most%20help.%20Sponsors%20contribute%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20month%2C%20which%20covers%20all%20expenses%2C%20including%20transportation%20(if%20needed)%2C%20books%2C%20and%20uniforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fs