urages%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20children%20between%20the%20ages%20of%200%20and%206%20by%20building%20on%20their%20strengths.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20work%20closely%20with%20special%20educators%20and%20therapists%20so%20they%20can%20carry%20out%20the%20activities%20practised%20during%20lessons%20at%20home.%20They%20are%20also%20given%20counselling%20services%20and%20support%20group%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaruna%20Vihar%20also%20focuses%20on%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20including%20theatre%20and%20creative%20interventions%20like%20exercises%20to%20help%20develop%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20functional%20skills.%20They%20also%20involve%20play%20in%20developing%20individualised%20education%20plans%20for%20each%20child%20to%20learn%20speech%20and%20language%20skills%20and%20alternative%20communication%20systems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encourage%20sensory%20stimulation%20and%20behaviour%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrucial%20aspects%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20Bishnoi%2C%20director%20of%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20at%20Latika%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20%E2%80%98inclusive%20education%E2%80%99%2C%20we%20also%20mean%20their%20inclusion%20in%20society.%20We%20have%20two%20catchwords%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98participation%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98opportunity%E2%80%99.%20I%20specifically%20work%20for%20the%20mainstreaming%20of%20our%20children%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20and%20the%20schools.%20Preparing%20the%20schools%20has%20become%20the%20main%20focus%20area%20for%20the%20inclusion%20team.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20commonplace%20in%20India%20for%20school%20managements%20to%20deny%20opportunities%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%2C%20and%20sometimes%20due%20to%20an%20unwillingness%20to%20%E2%80